_sText:
1024 cubed is a perfect cube with an internal dimension of 1024 units on each side.  There are multiple levels and it is symmetrical and balanced.  You can jump from the spawn to the basement pool or take multiple ladders to access any floor quickly.  It's a very bright map but less bright in the pool level.

All 36 spawn points work correctly, it's a small file and nav file included.  No buy zones included.
